      "content": "It's a very heavy thought, and the idea of \"letting go\" can sound like surrender, but sometimes it's actually a necessary act of self-preservation. If you are truly at a point where the effort outweighs any perceived reward, it might be time to let go of the *need* to fix everything right now. Please consider that stopping the struggle isn't giving up on life, but rather giving yourself permission to rest from the fight.",
